amp.name: Amp
amp.description:
Operator amp builds for different purposes

*Amps are player preference. There is no single 'best' for all content.*

**Void Angels:**
- 1x7/1x6 (if using Magus Melt)
- Madurai Focus
- Amp Arcanes: Eternal Eradicate + Eternal Onslaught
- Operator Arcane: Magus Melt

**Void Cascade:**
- 1x7/5x7
- Madurai Focus
- Amp Arcanes: Eternal Eradicate + Eternal Onslaught
- Operator Arcanes: Emergence Savior/Magus Lockdown/Magus Cloud

**Last Gasp & General Enemies (Raw damage):**
- 146 (sniper shot + homing glaive)/546 (3 round burst + homing glaive)/746 (flamethrower + homing glaive)
- Unairu or Madurai Focus (Unairu scales farther due to armor strip)
- Amp Arcanes: Eternal Onslaught + Virtuos Strike/Virtuos Tempo
- For Murmur: Virtuos Surge and Eternal Onslaught with Magus Melt for Radiation

**Viral application:**
- 646 (Apply Viral with prism, DPS with scaffold)
- Unairu Focus
- Amp Arcanes: Virtuous Trojan + Virtuos Ghost/Virtuos Tempo
- Operator Arcanes: Choice of Emergence Savior/Magus Lockdown/Magus Melt

-# from the [Warframe Community Discord](https://discord.gg/warframe)
